#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.63"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.63:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Arahantavagga → upādiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn22.63:0.2"
msgid "7. Arahantavagga "
msgstr "7. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 63. Upādiyamānasutta → arahattavaggo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.63:0.3"
msgid "63. Upādiyamānasutta "
msgstr "63. When You Grasp "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.74, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.63:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn22.63:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him, "

msgctxt "sn22.63:1.4"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṃkhittena dhammaṃ desetu yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:1.5"
msgid "“Upādiyamāno kho, bhikkhu, baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "“When you grasp, mendicant, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:1.6"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato”ti. "
msgstr "Not grasping, you’re free from the Wicked One.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:1.7"
msgid "“Aññātaṃ bhagavā, aññātaṃ sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“Understood, Blessed One! Understood, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.63:2.1"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do you see the detailed meaning of my brief statement?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:2.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, bhante, upādiyamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "“Sir, when you grasp form you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.3"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not grasping, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.4"
msgid "Vedanaṃ upādiyamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "When you grasp feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.5"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.6"
msgid "Saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.7"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ upādiyamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "consciousness, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:2.9"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not grasping, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:2.10"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.63:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu. "
msgstr "“Good, good, mendicant! "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.2"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi. "
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in brief like this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:3.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, bhikkhu, upādiyamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "When you grasp form you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.4"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not grasping, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.5"
msgid "Vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "When you grasp feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.6"
msgid "saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.7"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ upādiyamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "consciousness, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.63:3.9"
msgid "anupādiyamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not grasping, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:3.10"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti. "
msgstr "This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn22.63:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho so bhikkhu bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
msgstr "And then that mendicant approved and agreed with what the Buddha said. He got up from his seat, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before leaving. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:4.2"
msgid "Atha kho so bhikkhu eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharanto nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Then that mendicant, living alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute, soon realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. He lived having achieved with his own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.63:4.3"
msgid "“Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā”ti abbhaññāsi. "
msgstr "He understood: “Rebirth is ended; the spiritual journey has been completed; what had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of existence.” "

msgctxt "sn22.63:4.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca pana so bhikkhu arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And that mendicant became one of the perfected. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.63:4.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

